grid.text: 9. R. Simple pivot, Raise fan, Goes to 3.
3. R. Circle with pointed fan, facing the waki.
1. Circlet point 6. Waki turns facing front and point.

captions.translation: [JIUTAI] I will change into supernatural form.
Having changed into a supernatural form,
I will come without fail, at the appointed time,
and join you, adding my strength to yours.
captions.transcription: mairi aite onchikara wo tsuke mÅsubeshi.

captions.translation: So saying, into the evening clouds of Mt. Inari
without a sign of where he went, he vanished,
Without a sign of where he went, he vanished.
